Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
[Upper Body Workout and Stretching Exercises]

00:00:05.500 --> 00:00:07.000
[Upper Body Workout - Bow Pose]

00:00:07.500 --> 00:00:14.500
This helps to stretch the entire upper body, the shoulders, it opens up the chest

00:00:14.800 --> 00:00:18.000
It is a good stretch for your ankles and hip flexor.

00:00:21.000 --> 00:00:25.000
Lie chest down on the mat. 

00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:30.000
Keep your legs stretched and long.

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:35.000
Bend your right foot, take your right palm onto the ankle.

00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:37.500
Stretch the left arm out

00:00:37.500 --> 00:00:41.000
Inhale and lift yourself up.

00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:48.300
Hold your yoga posture for a few breaths

00:00:48.500 --> 00:00:52.000
Release down and switch to the other leg.

00:00:52.000 --> 00:00:58.000
Hold your ankle and reach the right palm and inhale.

00:00:58.000 --> 00:01:02.000
This completes the simple upper body workout - now, an advanced Upper Body Yoga - Full Bow Pose.

00:01:02.000 --> 00:01:06.000
Bring the feet together and bend at the knees

00:01:06.000 --> 00:01:10.000
Keep your palms on the ankle

00:01:10.000 --> 00:01:16.000
Get a nice firm grip, inhale and lift your body up.

00:01:16.000 --> 00:01:20.000
Get your knees and your chest off the mat

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:24.000
Only the hips and the abs touching the mat

00:01:24.300 --> 00:01:31.000
Knees together, stay here &amp; take a few breaths

00:01:31.300 --> 00:01:40.000
To release, relax the legs, bring the palms forward.

00:01:40.000 --> 00:01:42.000
That completes the full Upper Body Stretching and Workout

